title: Infestation (1, ZvR, Outbreak, 2) (IDW|2011-12|75% Dgtl|Various)
description:
Overview:

  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infestation_%28comics%29" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infestation_%28comics%29</a>

Contains:

   Infestation                01-02 (of 02) (digital-Empire)
   Transformers - Infestation 01-02 (of 02) (digital-Empire)
   Star Trek    - Infestation 01-02 (of 02) (Minutemen-DarthTremens)
   GI Joe       - Infestation 01-02 (of 02) (digital-Empire)
   Ghostbusters - Infestation 01-02 (of 02) (Minutemen-DarthTremens)
   Pocket God   - Infestation               (Digital) (Foyle-DCP)

   Zombies vs Robots - UnderCity 01-04 (of 04)       (digital-Empire)

   Infestation       - Outbreak  (Collected Edition) (Digital) (K6-Empire)

   Infestation 2                                01-02 (of 2)  (Digital-Nahga)
   Infestation 2 - Transformers                 01-02 (of 02) (digital-Empire)
   Infestation 2 - Dungeons and Dragons         01-02 (of 2)  (Digital-Nahga)
   Infestation 2 - Team-Up                                    (c2c) (Darthscanner)
   Infestation 2 - Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 1-2           (c2c) (Darthscanner)
   Infestation 2 - GI Joe                       01-02 (of 02) (Digital-HR) (Empire)
   Infestation 2 - 30 Days of Night                           (Digital-Nahga)

As surprisingly heterogeneous as this collection is (many are re-releases, so I'd
have expected a single scanner to tackle the whole cross-over), I'm fairly confident
that it's as good as can be for now and a lot better than any previously posted one.
